                        Ausstellers</rs>, 2. <rs type="person" ref="pe__peter_mannseber_QGW_II_I_1037">des Bergmeisters</rs>, 3. <rs type="person" ref="pe__stephan_popphinger_QGW_II_I_776">des. <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__lukas_popphinger_QGW_II_I_776">Bruders</roleName>
                        des Ausstellers Stephans des Popphinger</rs>, 4. <rs type="person" ref="pe__heinrich_oeler_QGW_II_I_771">seines <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__lukas_popphinger_QGW_II_I_776">swehers</roleName>
                        <roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Hainreichs des Öler</rs>.</rs></rs>
